               <msContents class="#CM">
                  <summary><p>A composite manuscript containing readings for Christian Festivals, taken from the Gospel. Described here as a multi-text manuscript for the sake of convenience.</p>
<p>Description based on the examination of the original (May 2021 and March 2022). The folios in the manuscript were in disorder and have been put back in the right order. The photos stored on Didomena show the two states of the manuscript (after and before).</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p>      </summary>
                  
